## Weather APP

This web application displays the weather conditions of a city along with an image of the city on Google Maps.

For enhanced security, the application employs Two-Factor Authentication (2FA). To register, users must provide a username and password, followed by scanning a QR code with the Google Authenticator app to receive a token that grants access to the application.

This application has been developed for educational purposes.

# Installation
To install the required dependencies, run the following command:

pip install -r requirements.txt

# Running the Application
To start the application, execute:

python app.py
